      "description": "This E46 M3 features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power delivery through individual throttle bodies and a high-revving valvetrain. Mated to a Getrag 6-speed manual and an M-Variable limited-slip differential, the drivetrain is robust and responsive. The suspension geometry remains precise with upgraded poly-bushings, and the critical rear subframe mounting points have been proactively reinforced. While the exterior shows minor road-derived patina, the mechanical synchronization and compression across all cylinders remain within tight tolerances. A mechanically sound enthusiast specimen optimized for driver engagement.",
